Articles.Content:
I get a crash when I cycle ships in space. This happens consistently if I cycle them at a normal speed. This is happening from deploying 4 probes and trying to control them.

The save file: https://www.dropbox.com/s/c5xzqi16cxcpilm/career.zip?dl=0

Mods required: Kerbal Engineer Redux, RemoteTech, Kerbal Construction Time

To reproduce: Load up in VAB the Alexander Graham Mk 1 ship, click launch and simulate. Go in orbit around kerbin at 80 km, and stage the probes away. Then cycle through ships with [ ].

KSP.log http://pastebin.com/VEexuB2W
